{"type": "article", "id": 2210, "title": "木制领结", "description": "", "date": "2014-09-07T22:36:47Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 2, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 3, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605222254A18BipyH20WkcVXT.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">谁说领结只能用纺织面料制作？总部位于底特律的 TAKD 设计工作室近日带来了他们的首款自己发起的设计项目——木质领结，主创希望能给传统的男士领结增添一些具有现代感的设计元素，他们选用了实木材质，整个制作过程全由手工制作、打磨而成，手工缝制的外部包裹面料提供 4 种花色可选，便于与任何外套、衬衫或裤装搭配使用。经过打磨的木制领结意外具有了复古的雅痞风格，绝对是秋冬季的绝佳搭配小物，定价 40 美元，</span><a href=\"http://takddesign.com/store.html\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里购买</a><span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726134922jvb6GON07SRT4q8e.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726134922LSd8UuqMbFw3TzZW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726134923UEF9XCTVtyJ7dNzo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}